        "content": "## 📚 SRE Runbooks\n\n### Incident Response Procedures\n- [Incident Response Guide](https://github.com/organization/repo/blob/main/docs/runbooks/INCIDENT_RESPONSE.md) - Escalation matrix, on-call procedures, incident lifecycle\n- [Rollback Procedures](https://github.com/organization/repo/blob/main/docs/runbooks/ROLLBACK_PROCEDURES.md) - Blue-green rollback, config rollback, database rollback\n\n### Debug Playbooks\n- [Latency Spike Debugging](https://github.com/organization/repo/blob/main/docs/runbooks/DEBUG_LATENCY_SPIKE.md) - Investigate and resolve high latency issues\n- [Memory Leak Debugging](https://github.com/organization/repo/blob/main/docs/runbooks/DEBUG_MEMORY_LEAK.md) - Identify and fix memory leak problems\n- [Circuit Breaker Debugging](https://github.com/organization/repo/blob/main/docs/runbooks/DEBUG_CIRCUIT_BREAKER.md) - Troubleshoot circuit breaker failures\n\n### Additional Resources\n- [Disaster Recovery Runbook](https://github.com/organization/repo/blob/main/DISASTER_RECOVERY_RUNBOOK.md)\n- [Multi-Region Failover Runbook](https://github.com/organization/repo/blob/main/docs/MULTI_REGION_FAILOVER_RUNBOOK.md)\n- [Platform Overview Dashboard](../platform-overview)\n- [Alertmanager Console](http://localhost:9093)\n\n---\n\n**On-Call Contact**: Check PagerDuty or internal wiki for current on-call rotation\n\n**Escalation**: For critical incidents, escalate to Platform Architect after 30 minutes",
